00:27:35.730 --> 00:27:37.030
&gt;&gt; Quick follow-up.

00:27:37.030 --> 00:27:38.330
&gt;&gt; Deborah Harkness: Yeah.

00:27:38.330 --> 00:27:39.630
&gt;&gt; Serpent's Mirror?

00:27:39.630 --> 00:27:40.930
&gt;&gt; Deborah Harkness:
So Serpent's Mirror.

00:27:40.930 --> 00:27:42.230
Who has questions about
