00:28:07.470 --> 00:28:11.230
and it brought me up short.

00:28:11.230 --> 00:28:14.240
And I started working on
the Marcus book as a kind

00:28:14.240 --> 00:28:18.310
of antidote as I worked
out the Matthew problem,

00:28:18.310 --> 00:28:20.590
and the Marcus book
was finished first.

00:28:20.590 --> 00:28:22.840
So I had a choice at that
