00:28:27.010 --> 00:28:28.310
[ Applause ]

00:28:28.310 --> 00:28:29.610
But Serpent's Mirror is coming.

00:28:29.610 --> 00:28:30.910
I promise.

00:28:30.910 --> 00:28:32.210
I promise.

00:28:32.210 --> 00:28:33.510
Yeah?

00:28:33.510 --> 00:28:34.810
&gt;&gt; First of all, I
