recommend for us?

00:35:50.830 --> 00:35:52.700
&gt;&gt; Deborah Harkness: Wow.

00:35:52.700 --> 00:35:54.370
So, you mean, just, like,
what are some of the books

00:35:54.370 --> 00:35:56.680
that I'm just loving
reading these days?

00:35:56.680 --> 00:35:57.980
&gt;&gt; Exactly.

00:35:57.980 --> 00:35:59.280
&gt;&gt; Deborah Harkness: So
I will tell you for --

00:35:59.280 --> 00:36:02.540
who has read Eleanor
