00:38:53.610 --> 00:38:56.520
to headache cures to apple pies.

00:38:56.520 --> 00:38:57.820
And I just love it.

00:38:57.820 --> 00:39:01.000
You know, but it was clearly
some household's essential text.

00:39:01.000 --> 00:39:03.110
&gt;&gt; Well, we have
a massive archive.

00:39:03.110 --> 00:39:09.780
So if you are needing
