00:39:11.140 --> 00:39:12.440
&gt;&gt; -- you can [inaudible] --

00:39:12.440 --> 00:39:13.740
&gt;&gt; Deborah Harkness: Perfect.

00:39:13.740 --> 00:39:15.040
&gt;&gt; -- on Facebook,
and [inaudible].

00:39:15.040 --> 00:39:16.340
&gt;&gt; Deborah Harkness: All right.

00:39:16.340 --> 00:39:17.640
I will come --

00:39:17.640 --> 00:39:18.940
&gt;&gt; Thank you.

00:39:18.940 --> 00:39:20.240
&gt;&gt; Deborah Harkness:
-- visit you.

00:39:20.240 --> 00:39:21.540
I'll take you up on that.

